{"tid":2058796,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"看似公平的初選機制","createTime":"2020-06-10T12:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T13:25:14.000Z","uid":47194,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"966a15aea0ae0c53fda37a0ac897aad9a8c0e83b","tid":2058796,"uid":47194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的，九月立法會選舉將舉行、大家都朝著35+的目標進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有人表示為了爭取最大公約數，集中票源到泛民候選人身上，提出了先舉行初選<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，避免到時互相票反讓建制有機可乘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原則上這論述合情合理，集中票源，一擊中的、但若細致研判，當中卻是大有文章。</strong></span></strong></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參加初選也需一定資源，但這種能耐獨立政治人物與一些政治素人根本不能擁有，在先天上他們已輸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；到了初選時，傳統泛民黨派的候選人挾黨派威名，不識人也識黨，外人根本難以抗衡，結果當然是泛民派出的初選名單「大勝」，所以竟然有媒體查詢，會否發生泛民大黨初選後不服輸呢？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>初選泛民黨派根本不會輸</strong><br />\n<br />\n公民黨主席楊岳橋表示，&hellip;.參與機制就必定要遵守承諾：「點會有得豁免呢？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />民主黨主席胡志偉表示「願賭服輸」，民協何啟明表示，若初選落敗的候選人不信守承諾照樣報名出選，肯定會被民情吞噬，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />這三大泛民黨派都說得正氣凜然，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為他們根本不會輸，既然不會輸當然「願賭服輸」，因為服輸的只會是外面的人。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>奪取政治道德高地</strong><br />\n<br />\n最近有位李佰盧的「政治素人」，發起「三不投」聯署，呼籲民主派選民聯署表態，拒絕在選舉中投票給「唔支持初選」、「唔參與初選」，以及「唔服從初選」的參選人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但如有人不支持「初選」也不參加「初選」，那如何叫人家服從結果呢？據悉這位李佰盧曾做過「雷動計劃」的義工，顯示他有一定的政治傾向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，三不投只會為泛民大黨增強政治光環，幸好據悉聯署人數只有五萬多人，不成氣候，否則真恐怖了，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不加入泛民大黨的遊戲就不能在政壇立足，但參加遊戲你不會贏。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>獨立人士難以出頭</strong><br />\n<br />\n不過無論「三不投」聯署的最後結果如何，九月立法會選舉泛民大黨將主控大局，不論初選如何「玩」，他們都掌握Q嘜認證，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>任何人拿著Q嘜就是泛民了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，別人來選就是「鬼」，來鎅票，建制B隊，叫你萬劫不復，如此政治素人與獨立人士將難在政圈出頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n民族自強，香港獨立</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/poExqy9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpoExqy9.png&h=d8e7a0c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9646e4755f97c78503b30f52e9949929400886a","tid":2058796,"uid":131282,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"熱狗不要再分化"},{"pid":"99130c97de7cc1a94d49204fbde0a9ea5d697bcc","tid":2058796,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9646e4755f97c78503b30f52e9949929400886a","tid":2058796,"uid":131282,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"熱狗不要再分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">［公投未來］全城罷工罷課 繼續集氣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2058733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2058733</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hk